OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTruss vows action on energy
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon first day as PM         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Liz Truss has promised to deal with    
OL,6, surging energy costs and to cut taxes, 
OL,7, after she won the Tory leadership      
OL,8, contest to become the next PM.         
OL,10,FHer plan, set to be announced on       
OL,11,FThursday, is likely to include a freeze
OL,12,Fon energy bills - though precisely how 
OL,13,Fit would work is still unclear.        
OL,15,FMs Truss will be formally appointed by 
OL,16,Fthe Queen at Balmoral Castle later,    
OL,17,Fafter a final speech by Boris Johnson. 
OL,19,FThe 47-year-old, the UK's third woman  
OL,20,FPM, will then appoint her cabinet.     
